To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private SeparatingLines _separatinglines;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_separatinglines = SeparatingLines(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_separatinglines.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "separatinglines", _separatinglines.Current.Value);
}
